    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Wisdom
---
Fools scatter about their many attributes, the wise keep such within; a
piece of straw floats upon the surface of water, a precious gemstone sinks
to the bottom. Therefore, it is best to disregard the seen and concentrate
upon the unseen. Only within the latter may riches be found.
